      <title>泰国空军计划预算 5.38 亿美元购买新型战斗机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/thai-air-force-eyes-538-million-budget-to-buy-new-fighter-jets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国空军计划从国家预算中寻求约 190 亿泰铢（5.38 亿美元）用于购买新战斗机以替换其老化的机队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/thai-air-force-eyes-538-million-budget-to-buy-new-fighter-jets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国公司希望香港停止谈论国家安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/us-firms-want-hong-kong-to-stop-talking-about-national-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港美国商会表示，在香港的美国公司希望这个曾经随心所欲的城市停止谈论国家安全，尽管它们面临着日益增长的地缘政治风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/us-firms-want-hong-kong-to-stop-talking-about-national-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 08:47:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军方预计需要 2024 年或更长时间才能消除哈马斯威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/israel-military-sees-long-road-ahead-to-eliminating-hamas-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方表示，他们正在加沙南部城市汗尤尼斯进行迄今为止最激烈的战斗，他们希望在那里杀死或抓获据信与人质一起躲藏在隧道中的哈马斯领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/israel-military-sees-long-road-ahead-to-eliminating-hamas-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 08:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾计划四月份扩大与美国的军事演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/philippines-eyes-expanded-military-drills-with-us-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾和美国计划在四月份举行可能是两国最大规模的军事演习，以在南海紧张局势加剧之际展示两国联盟的实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/philippines-eyes-expanded-military-drills-with-us-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 07:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑对致命袭击作出反应之际，伊朗敦促采取外交手段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/iran-urges-diplomacy-as-us-weighs-response-to-deadly-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗敦促美国利用外交手段缓解中东紧张局势，德黑兰准备对周末针对美国基地的致命袭击做出军事反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/iran-urges-diplomacy-as-us-weighs-response-to-deadly-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 06:53:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府计划采取新措施平息农民抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/french-government-plans-new-measures-to-calm-farmer-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着抗议者继续封锁巴黎周边的高速公路，法国政府计划周二采取新措施，解决农民对成本上升和欧洲法规的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/french-government-plans-new-measures-to-calm-farmer-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北爱尔兰协议似乎将结束英国脱欧的政治僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dup-to-end-brexit-boycott-restore-power-sharing-in-n-ireland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主统一党同意结束对北爱尔兰权力分享议会的抵制，结束了两年来导致该地区无法做出政策决定并阻止英国首相里希·苏纳克政府结束脱欧进程的政治瘫痪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dup-to-end-brexit-boycott-restore-power-sharing-in-n-ireland</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 01:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港国安法扩大国家秘密的定义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/hong-kong-s-leader-to-announce-consultation-on-new-security-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港领导人公布了一项通过香港国安法的广泛计划，其中将包括类似中国的国家机密定义，并加大力度防范外国干涉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/hong-kong-s-leader-to-announce-consultation-on-new-security-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 01:24:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相在选举讨论中推动提高工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/japan-pm-keeps-up-push-for-higher-wages-as-election-talk-swirls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄继续推进提高工资的运动，因为他的支持率下滑似乎已经停止，并且重新出现了他可能选择今年举行大选的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/japan-pm-keeps-up-push-for-higher-wages-as-election-talk-swirls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 23:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国寻求对致命的中东袭击做出足够强硬的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/us-seeks-a-just-tough-enough-response-to-deadly-mideast-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员和专家表示，美国总统乔·拜登的政府正在寻求对驻约旦美军遭到致命袭击的回应，这种回应足以威慑伊朗及其代理人，而又不会引发与伊斯兰共和国的直接战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/us-seeks-a-just-tough-enough-response-to-deadly-mideast-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:55:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
